---
---

<section class="relative py-24 lg:py-32 overflow-hidden" style="background:#020817;">
  <!-- Grid de fondo -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(59,130,246,0.12) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(59,130,246,0.12) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:40px 40px;opacity:0.6;"></div>
  <!-- Gradiente radial azulado -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="background:radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 50%,rgba(37,99,235,0.15) 0%,transparent 70%);"></div>

  <div class="relative px-8 mx-auto md:px-12 lg:px-24 max-w-7xl">
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:text-balance mb-12">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-6 border" style="background:rgba(59,130,246,0.12);border-color:rgba(59,130,246,0.3);color:#60a5fa;">
        <span aria-hidden="true">🚀</span>
        TESTIMONIOS
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6 tracking-tight" style="color:#f0f6ff;">
        Lo que dicen nuestros clientes
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed" style="color:rgba(240,246,255,0.7);">
        Casos reales de empresas que han mejorado su operativa con IA.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <!-- Testimonio 1 -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 group" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.18);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);">
        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
          {[1,2,3,4,5].map(() => (
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="#fbbf24" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="text-base font-medium leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color:rgba(240,246,255,0.8);">
          "El chatbot nos ha quitado mucha carga de trabajo repetitivo. Ahora el equipo puede dedicarse a casos que realmente requieren atención personalizada."
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl flex-shrink-0" style="background:rgba(59,130,246,0.15);border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.25);">👤</div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-bold" style="color:#f0f6ff;">Laura Martínez</p>
            <p class="text-xs" style="color:rgba(240,246,255,0.5);">Responsable de Atención al Cliente</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonio 2 -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 group" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.18);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);">
        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
          {[1,2,3,4,5].map(() => (
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="#fbbf24" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="text-base font-medium leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color:rgba(240,246,255,0.8);">
          "La gestión de citas era un caos. Desde que implementamos el sistema, tenemos menos llamadas y los clientes pueden reservar 24/7."
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl flex-shrink-0" style="background:rgba(129,140,248,0.15);border:1px solid rgba(129,140,248,0.25);">👤</div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-bold" style="color:#f0f6ff;">Javier López</p>
            <p class="text-xs" style="color:rgba(240,246,255,0.5);">Propietario de Clínica Dental</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonio 3 -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 group" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.18);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);">
        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
          {[1,2,3,4,5].map(() => (
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="#fbbf24" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/></svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="text-base font-medium leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color:rgba(240,246,255,0.8);">
          "Buscar documentos en carpetas compartidas nos llevaba horas. Ahora encontramos cualquier información en segundos. Simple pero efectivo."
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl flex-shrink-0" style="background:rgba(74,222,128,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(74,222,128,0.22);">👤</div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-bold" style="color:#f0f6ff;">Ana Ruiz</p>
            <p class="text-xs" style="color:rgba(240,246,255,0.5);">Coordinadora de Proyectos</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
